data.description: Discover the elegance of townhouse living where charm meets convenience in this stunning three bedroom, three bathroom residence nestled in the private gated community of Montacino. The Spanish style roof, arched entryway, and paver driveway invite you inside, leading to a one car garage perfect for secure parking or additional storage. As you step through the front door, foyer greets you with a convenient half bath perfect for accommodating guests. Tile flooring throughout the first level reflects an air of cleanliness and style, guiding you to the heart of the home. The kitchen is a home chef's delight, boasting shaker cabinets adorned with crown molding, chic tile backsplash, lustrous granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and a pantry closet for optimal storage. Bar top seating offers a casual dining experience, while the adjacent dining room illuminated by an elegant chandelier sets the stage for memorable meals. The spacious living room, a canvas for relaxation and entertainment, opens up to a covered back porch through a glass door, marrying indoor comfort with outdoor tranquility. Ascend to the second floor where the primary suite becomes a sanctuary of peace, featuring a ceiling fan with crystal chandelier accents, a walk in closet, a sun drenched balcony, and an en suite bathroom. The bathroom showcases dual vanities with ample counter space, wood style flooring, and a lavish rainfall shower with bench seating. Two additional bedrooms ensure comfort for family and friends, complemented by a full guest bath and a convenient laundry closet with cabinet storage. Outside, a large grassy common area beckons for leisurely walks with pets or impromptu picnics. The community itself offers a refreshing swimming pool, adding to the allure of this charming abode. Located with quick access to I-4, downtown Orlando, and Cranes Roost, shopping and attractions. Your options for recreation and entertainment are endless. Lace up your skates at the Orlando Ice Den, kayak down Wekiva Springs, take a walk through the botanical gardens, catch a concert at the nearby stadium, and savor the delicious restaurants in the area. Seize the opportunity to make this home your own—schedule a showing and experience the blend of luxury and convenience that awaits you!
